Data Types:
1. Boolean 
2. Numeric 
3. String
4. Derived
    Pointer 
    Array 
    Structure 
    Union 
    Function 
    Slice 
    Interface 
    Map 
    Channel


Variable:
var  i, j, k int;
var  c, ch byte;
var  f, salary float32;
d =  42;
d = 3, f = 5;
var a, b, c = 3, 4, "foo"  

Constants (literals)
Constants are treated just like regular variables except that their values cannot be modified after their definition.
const LENGTH int = 10
